http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/puducherry/ISES-admission-test-on-February-7/article13994943.ece

The Lycée Français of Puducherry has announced the test for admission to its International Section of Excellence in Science (ISES) on February 7 for the academic year 2016-17.The ISES is targeted at students who are exceptional in science enter the equivalent of class IX and complete schooling with a Baccalauréat specialised in science, the diploma awarded by the French Ministry of Education.The ISES also gives students an opportunity to compete for the Bourse d’Excellence Major, a scholarship for higher education in France.The school also has modules for non-French speaking students (6 to 14 years old) to help their integration into the French educational system.